description:
This is the first of the three versions of the concerto.

I. Allegro vivace (alla breve)
II. Largo
III. Allegro vivace.
Performed by Alexandre Ghindin (piano) with the Helsinki Philharmonic Orchestra conducted by Vladimir Ashkenazy.
